body.description: Simplify your plumbing projects and provide everything you need for a fast and easy dishwasher installation with the 6 feet dishwasher hook up kit. The supply line features a PVC core, multi-filament braided nylon reinforcement, a clear vinyl outer shell, and a grade 304 corrosion-resistant stainless steel braided exterior that is designed to prevent kinking and crimping. The dishwasher adapter kit comes with a 3-prong angled power cord, 3/8 inch male iron pipe elbow and a 3/4 inch female hose elbow. The supply line in this dishwasher connection kit is lead-free compliant for potable water applications, and is UPC approved and CSA certified.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great kit but keen eye needed!
reviews.reviewText: Everything you need when installing a new dishwasher. A few extra parts that were not needed but nice to have for a future project.One star deduction for unclear wiring. The wire provided does not have your typical white, black green wire indicators of insulation to wire easily. The green wire was identified easily but the white/black wires took some digging to find out. The wire line with the indention on the side, it takes a keen eye to see, is the hot wire. Also, after looking carefully, looking at the three-prong plug, there was a 'w' which indicated white. I used these notifications as a guide to properly hook it up. Other than that, a great kit for the inexperienced dishwasher installer.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars All the parts needed for a new dishwasher connection, at a great price.
reviews.reviewText: EZ-Flow 48337 Dishwasher Installation Kit is hard to beat. All the parts I needed to wire and [supply] plumb my new dishwasher. There are a variety of plumbing adapters so the kit fits both those with a "garden hose / washer" style inlet, and also also fits 3/8" compression style inlet. Typical stainless braid over the 6 ft hose. Note, the power cord has "SPT-3 105C° 16AWGX3C" embedded in the cord. Some reviews here were complaining that the wire gauge was inadequate for a dishwasher connection. My Fridigaire FFBD2412SS dishwasher specification document says its "Total Amp Draw = 10.0". And 16AWG wire is rated for up to 13 amps, so the ampacity of the included cord is perfectly adequate for this dishwasher. And vendor "Faucets and Accesories" shipped my order very quickly.
